OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy but dry and bright at first.
OL,7,FCloud will thicken from the west,
OL,8,Fbringing a few spots of rain through
OL,9,Fthe early hours, though southern areas
OL,10,Fare likely to remain dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FGenerally cloudy but largely
OL,13,Fdry at first, with any rain confined
OL,14,Fmainly to higher ground. However, slow-
OL,15,Fmoving showers will develop during the
OL,16,Fafternoon, potentially heavy locally
OL,17,Fbefore clearing eastwards later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
