OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFairly
OL,6,Fcloudy with isolated showers on
OL,7,FWednesday, some sunshine developing
OL,8,Flater. A wet and windy start on
OL,9,FThursday, drier and brighter later.
OL,10,FDry with sunny spells on Friday,
OL,11,Fthough breezy.
